{"tid":924572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有心不怕難】22歲唐氏綜合症患者，靠賣襪年賺600萬美元！","createTime":"2018-12-02T08:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T02:28:06.000Z","uid":212399,"like":673,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"c840a1ee881c12b6aba6239adae37761b89269a4","tid":924572,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Downsyndrom525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FDownsyndrom525.jpg&h=dde720a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在紐約位於長島的小鎮，有數十個整齊有序的箱子，架子上擺著色彩繽紛、各式各樣的襪子，有俏皮印花、印有加拿大總理的臉的襪子、也有看起來像梵高的《星夜》的襪子等。22歲的John Cronin便是靠賣這些襪子，年賺600萬美元（下同）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/螢幕快照-2018-11-30-下午6.45.38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-11-30-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%886.45.38.jpg&h=d6fa6e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJohn Cronin是一位唐氏綜合症患者，高中畢業後便開始萌生起工作的念頭。有別於常人，John的選擇有限，沒有太多僱主願意為唐氏綜合症患者提供工作機會，通常他們都只能從事零售業。John對零售業的興趣不大，卻擁有一顆渴望創業的心，便打算與父親一同做生意。<br />\n靈感來自「世界唐氏綜合症日」<br />\nJohn的創業靈感來自「世界唐氏綜合症日」，即是每年的3月21日（這個日期象徵著21號染色體的三倍，導致唐氏綜合症）。在傳統上，人們會穿著有趣的圖案和和瘋狂顏色的襪子來慶祝這個日子。然而，在坊間很難找到特別慶祝唐氏綜合症的襪子。於是，他專為這個日子設計了一款襪子，上面有紫色心臟、「3-21」的圖案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/螢幕快照-2018-11-30-下午6.47.29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-11-30-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%886.47.29.jpg&h=5547c374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起初，Cronin父子在業務上投資了數千元，在網上售賣襪子，並在Facebook拍片宣傳。2016年12月，他們正式推出J ohn's Crazy Socks網站，提供31種不同設計的襪子，每雙5至12元不等。然而該網站卻意外出了問題。雖然有所延誤，但他們在第一天仍收到42份訂單，全部都是當地人。於是，John便要想法子把襪子送到買家手上。<br />\n用誠意打動人心<br />\n當時，John決定送貨上門，他把訂單襪子都整齊地用薄紙包裹，並用紅色盒子包裝，上面寫著感謝信和糖果。人們都被他的誠意所打動，甚至和John一起拍照、拍攝短片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Bush-Socks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FBush-Socks.jpg&h=7b9d818f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這些影片和照片開始在社交媒體上傳播，並為他帶來大量訂單。第一個月，他們發出了452份訂單，收入約為13,000元，而銷情最好的是他們的慈善襪子。每對慈善襪子銷售的2美元都會捐贈給公司的慈善合作夥伴，而John's Crazy Socks也將其收入的5％捐贈給特奧會。<br />\n目前為止，John's Crazy Socks創造了35個工作崗位，僱用了不同能力的人，包括患有自閉症、唐氏綜合症的人。今年，它們的訂單量達到160,000至180,000，收入超過600萬元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/11/30/article/84894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2018%2F11%2F30%2Farticle%2F84894&d=ANChfUt99FUJmRYkrR0xNk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c8fb1df9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/11/30/article/84894</a>"},{"pid":"20d217d4b628f7a62446bafd185f27cb87666fb1","tid":924572,"uid":212399,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6359fae65345699e1969f480884af7d107ee3d9d","tid":924572,"uid":94828,"like":17,"dislike":300,"score":-283,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:11:18.000Z","msg":"咪又靠父幹"},{"pid":"83629e4b6d0f1ed0e29d64d87f5c1a76be921a73","tid":924572,"uid":7343,"like":617,"dislike":13,"score":604,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:13:42.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傻既都搵得多過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傻都不如"},{"pid":"a3a57a3aa0003d292456bd1e6080b3e58e9a5bc1","tid":924572,"uid":93284,"like":791,"dislike":6,"score":785,"quote":{"pid":"63